  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the gate got immediately closed and locked.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they didn't search inside the gate, inside the-- which was an absolute luck out of this world for me particularly, because what happened was that in the-- when I came into the gate, somebody who was immediately after me threw me down, and I lost the-- the hand of my cousin, and she run ahead, and they still heard the screaming came from her [GERMAN] which means Stefan.",
      "word_count": 69
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was [GERMAN], and she was disappearing into the yard somehow, because she was pulled probably by the other cousin.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I got up and still-- there were still some people who burst in and somebody I was thrown down second time in the middle of this passage.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I got up again, and there was nobody already in front of me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the gate was closed and, of course, my first instinct was to hide as quickly as possible, really like an animal instinct more than anything.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I started looking for a place to hide.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went into the first staircase, and I tried to go down, and there was the bakery.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And people were pushing me out, because they didn't want me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I went to somewhere else, and people were again pushing me out, because those people, they were probably still living there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were thinking, you know, people who are already in their umschlag or on their way to umschlagplatz they were somehow already-- they were already sick with plague.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were already-- you didn't probably-- that's probably-- so they pushed me out of the bakery and they-- and then I tried to hide in some other cellar, and I didn't manage either.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was running around.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
